{"tid":2208733,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"尼日利亞一州立法：強姦犯不論男女會被手術閹割　性侵兒童者處死","createTime":"2020-09-19T06:49:13.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-19T14:46:33.000Z","uid":333488,"like":230,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":67,"replies":[{"pid":"706ae5c7c1316fd66f860f4b14d99f57dfad2cf4","tid":2208733,"uid":333488,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:49:13.000Z","msg":"位於尼日利亞北部的卡杜納州（Kaduna state），州議會本周通過的修例相當嚴厲：強姦罪名成立的成年男子將被手術閹割。如他性侵犯的是兒童，甚至會被判處死刑。如對兒童下手的是女子，她的輸卵管會被摘除。<br />\n男性倘性侵犯14歲以下兒童會被判處死刑，死前其睪丸會被割去；即使受害人已成年，強姦犯也會被閹割，以及被判終身監禁。<br />\n<br />\n修例尚未通過之前，州內成年強姦犯的最高刑罰是入獄21年，性侵兒童者判處無期徒刑。<br />\n<br />\n卡杜納州長魯法伊（Nasir Ahmad el-Rufai）表示：「嚴厲的刑罰有助於進一步保護兒童免受嚴重罪行所害。」魯法伊16日簽署法案讓它生效。<br />\n<br />\n這麼做不是所有人都讚賞，有持批評意見的人認為這是民粹之舉，也不合符憲法。而且有人預期，這可能導致更少案件曝光。<br />\n<br />\n呢次真係切JJ<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/article/525721?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2Farticle%2F525721%3Futm_source%3D01appshare%26utm_medium%3Dreferral&d=QA0Qo2zDcB%2FuI%2B3HtJ%2FdCjYSMhv%2BBpubH8pt7agTF2U%3D&h=8baefa36\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/article/525721?utm_source=01appshare&amp;utm_medium=referral</a>"},{"pid":"d234029928b75c8e783bcf5cd6e9e2de99d07ecf","tid":2208733,"uid":25858,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:49:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a861cd66326a27e8dbcbab67fde8c0e55e061015","tid":2208733,"uid":165336,"like":2,"dislike":10,"score":-8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-09-19T06:51:33.000Z","msg":"聽講男人做手術痛過女人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji